###############################################################
---------------------
PYRHARCKADE 1.0B OPEN
---------------------
###############################################################

Beofre : 

You have to verify the bin path of the script PYRHARCKADE/bin/MAME.sh
You have to verify the bin path of the script PYRHARCKADE/bin/get_media.sh
You have to verify the bin path of the script PYRHARCKADE/bin/verif_roms.sh

-----------------------------------------------------------------


First step : create your file from the liste of roms you can get on :

	http://pyrharckade.tuxme.net/roms/

Get the file and replace the ROM_CONFIG_FILES.csv in the / of PYRHARCKADE



------------------------------------------------------------------

Seconf step : start PYR in the PYRHARCKADE/ directory :
cd ${HOME}/PYRHARCKADE/
./start.py

and use in the config menu : GET MEDIA + VERIF ROMS

This scripts genreate a correct ROM_CONFIG_FILE and get the folowing 
media in the good path of the PYRHARCKADE FE : 

	* roms
	* snap
	* video
	* wheel
	* doc 

------------------------------------------------------------------

To start PYRHARCKADE :

go to cd ${HOME}/PYRHARCKADE/
and use start.py

./start.py

Pour lancer en mode vertical :

./start.py [YES/NO] Y


------------------------------------------------------------------

Note for the pi version :

